---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service | Marketing Company Edinburgh" description="Our business terms for providing marketing services to our Edinburgh-based clients.">
	<section class="py-32 bg-slate-50">
		<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
			<h1 class="text-5xl font-black text-[#0A192F] mb-12">Terms of Service</h1>
			<div class="prose prose-lg prose-slate max-w-none 
				prose-headings:text-[#0A192F] prose-headings:font-black 
				prose-p:text-gray-600 prose-p:leading-relaxed 
				prose-strong:text-[#0A192F]">
				<p>Last Updated: April 9, 2026</p>
				<h2>1. Service Agreements</h2>
				<p>Our services are provided on a project or retainer basis as outlined in your specific contract with Marketing Company Edinburgh. These terms govern the relationship between our agency and your business.</p>
				<h2>2. Professional Standards</h2>
				<p>We adhere to the highest industry standards for digital marketing, ensuring all campaigns are implemented ethically and in compliance with platform guidelines (Google, Meta, etc.).</p>
				<h2>3. Payment and Billing</h2>
				<p>Invoices are issued according to your agreed schedule and are payable within the specified timeframe. Late payments may result in the suspension of active campaigns.</p>
				<h2>4. Confidentiality</h2>
				<p>All client data and business strategies shared with us are treated with strict confidentiality and will never be shared with third parties without your explicit consent.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
